        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "CALL IMMEDIATELY (Critical Emergencies):\n- Sparking, smoking, or burning smell from electrical equipment\n- Well pump electrical failure (no water in extreme heat)\n- Exposed or downed electrical wires\n- Water flooding from electrical equipment areas\n- Generator won't start during extended power outage\n- Electrical fire or active arcing\n- Shock hazard from outlets, switches, or equipment\n- Panel that's hot, buzzing, or showing visible damage\n- Lightning strike damage to electrical system\n\nSame-Day Service Needed:\n- Repeated breaker trips affecting critical circuits\n- Voltage problems causing equipment malfunction\n- Well pump operating intermittently\n- Preparing for extreme weather requiring reliable electrical\n- New livestock depending on electrical water systems\n- Workshop or barn electrical problems affecting operations\n\nSchedule Routine Service:\n- Annual electrical safety inspections\n- Planned panel upgrades\n- Adding circuits for workshop or equipment\n- Generator preventive maintenance\n- Pre-purchase electrical inspections\n- Code compliance for insurance\n- EV charger or solar preparation"
